title: Lisa Jackson-Fatal Burn
description: New York Times best-selling author Lisa Jackson revives two characters from her popular novel Deep Freeze (RB#L1127) in this sequel. Her heart-pounding crime novels are famous for their thrilling romances, and Fatal Burn turns up the heat. Last time we met her, Shannon Flannery struggled to prove her innocence when blamed for her husbands death. Now Shannon is sure someone is trying to kill her, but the only person who believes her is ................
